Package: cat.ademic
Title: Academic Paper Classification with LLMs
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Chris", "Soria", role = c("aut", "cre"),
                  email = "chris.soria@nyu.edu")
Description: R interface to the Python catademic package. Classifies, extracts,
    explores, and summarizes academic papers using LLMs. A thin domain wrapper
    around cat.stack that adds journal and topic sourcing parameters for
    academic literature analysis.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
Imports:
    reticulate (>= 1.28),
    cat.stack (>= 0.1.0)
Suggests:
    testthat (>= 3.0.0)
Config/testthat/edition: 3
